    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project or a source for parts. The exterior has visible rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and the clear coat is peeling significantly. Mechanically, the engine runs but suffers from a rough idle and a noticeable oil leak, while the suspension feels loose and will likely need a complete overhaul. Inside, the upholstery is torn in multiple places and several electronic components, including the radio and rear power windows, are non-functional. It will require a trailer for transport as it is not currently roadworthy.",
