      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all project seekers and DIY enthusiasts! This car is the ultimate canvas for your next restoration journey. While it's currently in poor condition and will require some dedicated mechanical and cosmetic work, it represents a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity to build something truly yours from the ground up. If you love getting your hands dirty and bringing life back to a vehicle, this is the one for you!",
